<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 18:14:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>耶伦表示中国可能对美国的关税行动做出回应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/yellen-says-chinese-response-possible-expected-us-tariff-action-2024-05-13/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周一表示，在美国采取任何关税行动后，美国可能会看到中国做出重大反应，预计本周将针对某些行业征收新关税。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 15:06:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/yellen-says-chinese-response-possible-expected-us-tariff-action-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>麦当劳在报告食品问题后与中国监管机构合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mcdonalds-cooperating-with-chinese-regulator-after-reported-food-issues-2024-05-13/</link><description>麦当劳周一在其中文网站上表示，该公司正在积极配合中国当地市场监管机构对食品问题相关事宜进行调查核实。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 14:55:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mcdonalds-cooperating-with-chinese-regulator-after-reported-food-issues-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟将放弃对中国竞标罗马尼亚太阳能园区的调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-drop-probe-into-chinese-bidders-romanian-solar-park-2024-05-13/</link><description>欧洲工业委员会蒂埃里·布雷顿(Thierry Breton)周一表示，在中国企业退出罗马尼亚太阳能园区公开招标后，欧盟委员会将结束对这些公司的调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 12:38:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-drop-probe-into-chinese-bidders-romanian-solar-park-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国新冠举报人入狱四年后将获释</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-covid-whistleblower-due-release-after-4-years-jail-2024-05-13/</link><description>预计中国当局将于周一释放一名被判入狱四年的公民记者，她记录了 2020 年中部城市武汉冠状病毒爆发的早期阶段。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 12:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-covid-whistleblower-due-release-after-4-years-jail-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国本周启动1万亿元刺激性债券发行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-kick-off-1-trillion-yuan-stimulus-bond-issues-this-week-2024-05-13/</link><description>中国财政部计划本周开始筹集期待已久的1万亿元人民币（合1380亿美元）的长期特别国债，以筹集资金用于刺激疲软经济的关键领域。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 11:22:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-kick-off-1-trillion-yuan-stimulus-bond-issues-this-week-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：盈利障碍已清除 - 接下来消费者物价指数将上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-13/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 10:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟要求 Booking.com 必须遵守严格的技术规则，并对 X 进行调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-says-booking-must-comply-with-strict-tech-rules-investigates-x-2024-05-13/</link><description>欧盟委员会周一表示，已将酒店预订网站 Booking.com 指定为“看门人”，使其承担严格的欧盟义务，并已展开调查，以进一步确定社交媒体网络 X 的监管状况。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 09:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-says-booking-must-comply-with-strict-tech-rules-investigates-x-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>尽管“困难”，中国仍呼吁与韩国保持稳定关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-koreas-top-diplomat-warns-rising-economic-competition-with-china-2024-05-13/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周一在北京举行的一次罕见会议上对韩国外长表示，尽管中韩两国最近面临“困难”，但仍应寻求稳定的关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 09:30:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-koreas-top-diplomat-warns-rising-economic-competition-with-china-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>中美在日内瓦会面讨论人工智能风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-china-meet-geneva-discuss-ai-risks-2024-05-13/</link><description>美国和中国将于周二在日内瓦会面讨论人工智能，美国官员强调，华盛顿的政策不会进行谈判，因为谈判将探讨如何减轻新兴技术的风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 09:04:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-china-meet-geneva-discuss-ai-risks-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国新关税对中国电动汽车和其他出口产品的打击有多大？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/how-hard-will-new-biden-tariffs-hit-china-2024-05-13/</link><description>据知情人士透露，美国总统乔·拜登将于周二宣布对中国征收新关税，目标包括电动汽车、医疗用品和太阳能设备等行业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 08:57:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/how-hard-will-new-biden-tariffs-hit-china-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>德国称 2023 年外国行为者的网络犯罪增加了 28%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germany-says-cybercrime-by-foreign-actors-rose-by-28-2023-2024-05-13/</link><description>周一发布的数据显示，2023 年德国外国犯罪者的网络犯罪激增，比上一年增长了 28%，而欧洲在选举前夕对涉嫌俄罗斯黑客和间谍的担忧加剧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 08:49:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germany-says-cybercrime-by-foreign-actors-rose-by-28-2023-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>“选择法国”投资推动承诺创纪录的 160 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/france-gets-16-billion-foreign-investments-part-choose-france-event-2024-05-13/</link><description>周一，法国赢得了创纪录的 150 亿欧元（161.7 亿美元）外国投资承诺，让法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 得以在全球首席执行官的聚光灯下，暂时忘记紧张的公共财政和疲弱的民意调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 04:03:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/france-gets-16-billion-foreign-investments-part-choose-france-event-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行承诺支持经济复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-pledges-support-economic-recovery-2024-05-10/</link><description>中国央行周五表示，将确保流动性合理充裕和信贷扩张，巩固经济复苏，但经济复苏仍面临诸多挑战。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 17:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-pledges-support-economic-recovery-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>独家：Shein 在美国上市遇到障碍的情况下加紧伦敦 IPO 准备工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shein-steps-up-london-ipo-preparations-amid-us-hurdles-listing-sources-say-2024-05-10/</link><description>消息人士称，如果此次IPO成功，可能会成为今年全球规模最大的IPO之一。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 16:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shein-steps-up-london-ipo-preparations-amid-us-hurdles-listing-sources-say-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商 Zeekr 在美国市场首次亮相，股价飙升近 35%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-zeekr-set-debut-nyse-after-upsized-ipo-2024-05-10/</link><description>周五，Zeekr 的股价较首次公开募股价格上涨近 35%，这为这家电动汽车制造商带来了强劲的开局，这是自 2021 年以来首家中国公司在美国主要市场首次亮相。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 10:48:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-zeekr-set-debut-nyse-after-upsized-ipo-2024-05-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>